WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:03.166
Grandma, this is the meal I stayed up late to make.

2
00:00:03.166 --> 00:00:04.566
It's my blood.

3
00:00:04.966 --> 00:00:07.633
Lin Zhiwei, what do you say?

4
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:09.800
You belong to the Lin family

5
00:00:10.166 --> 00:00:12.533
All your achievements belong to the company

6
00:00:12.533 --> 00:00:13.700
Belongs to the Lin family

7
00:00:14.166 --> 00:00:16.300
Then you have disappointed me so much.

8
00:00:17.066 --> 00:00:18.400
You're fired.

9
00:00:18.700 --> 00:00:21.633
The company doesn't need a disobedient person like you

10
00:00:21.966 --> 00:00:25.000
Then why don't you get out?

11
00:00:30.066 --> 00:00:30.866
Linlin

12
00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:35.766
Are you sure you can connect with Haiyue Group?

13
00:00:35.766 --> 00:00:37.766
Oh, it's my fault.

14
00:00:37.866 --> 00:00:39.300
Our contract with Haiyue Group

15
00:00:39.300 --> 00:00:41.200
Then it's all gone

16
00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:42.800
Don't worry, grandma.

17
00:00:43.533 --> 00:00:45.233
Documents are readily available

18
00:00:45.366 --> 00:00:46.566
No problem.

19
00:00:51.900 --> 00:00:54.066
Sister, what's the matter with you?

20
00:00:56.700 --> 00:00:58.300
Did grandma bully you again?

21
00:00:59.566 --> 00:01:02.066
The planning case I worked on for more than half a month

22
00:01:02.066 --> 00:01:04.466
Grandma settled the claim without saying a word

23
00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:06.266
Kicked me out of the company

24
00:01:06.700 --> 00:01:08.200
How could they do this?

25
00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:11.066
So hateful, sister, don't be sad.

26
00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:13.966
I'm going to find them now to vent my anger for you

27
00:01:15.466 --> 00:01:16.466
What are you good for?

28
00:01:16.466 --> 00:01:19.066
Wife, leave this matter to me.

29
00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:22.266
I won't let them cry and beg you to come back

